{"tid":614291,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)3X反恐暴族3 怒海救援 監獄格鬥4 2 3","createTime":"2018-04-02T11:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T18:23:39.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b90d8f1897cbe4db0771504dbc0208f3e4495e8","tid":614291,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=00c316aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=96fc5b33\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/78/XXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F78%2FXXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg&h=4b8400dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1_Pf5RP_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1_Pf5RP_1200x0.jpg&h=cf7b68f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/88/1b/e6/881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F88%2F1b%2Fe6%2F881be6155294dff3b41fc98dd1220837.jpg&h=560d881c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://outalpha.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/CZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foutalpha.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FCZvKWAKWwAEQcAt-e1472162325808.jpg&h=47f076bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述從極限運動員變成政府特工的桑德&middot;凱吉本被認為已死亡，但因致命戰士翔與他的團隊企圖利用危險的潘多拉盒子為非作歹，使得桑德&middot;凱吉再次被找上，組成新團隊來阻止；而他也發現自己將陷入世界各國政府高層間的勾結和陰謀中..<br />\n<br />\n2.改編自真實災難事件，一場規模空前的風暴在美國東北角掀起駭人狂風和滔天巨浪，兩艘大型油輪就在狂風暴雨中撞裂成兩半。一組海岸防衛隊冒著生命危險，在零下低溫和70英尺的巨浪威脅下，靠著單薄的救生艇，要與時間和天氣競賽，搶救岌岌可危的油輪組員性命..<br />\n<br />\n3.犯人戰士尤裏?伯伊卡（斯科特阿金斯 飾）霸氣回歸!依然要參加格鬥賽!然而這一部裏，當他把對手解決掉後，對手意外死亡，這也讓他重新審視自己參賽的意義，尤其發現遺孀被幕後黑手控制，他要爲她的自由而戰!不過這次的對手更難對付了!<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述在前集過後的數年，前世界重量級拳王喬治&middot;「冰人」&middot;錢伯為了在退休時間賺點錢，便而前往俄羅斯拍廣告。在造訪當地進行的一系列的拳擊比賽時，他遭他人誣陷持有古柯鹼，而再度被送往監獄，但那裡的氣候卻比以前待的監獄還要寒冷。<br />\n在那他發現了該監獄官員安排的非法綜合格鬥賽，以助在外的大亨賺取賭金。為此，冰人與背後的大亨達成協議，只要打倒獄中最強的戰士尤里&middot;波卡就能重獲自由。但身手高超的幫派頭目尤里&middot;波卡為了成為世界最強的拳手，而與冰人不合，使得雙方的暴力戰役即將展開..<br />\n<br />\n5.故事敘述繼前集的數年過後，右膝受傷的失去戰力的尤里&middot;波卡因自卑而引退，而改至廁所打掃。但因黑幫老大兼監獄格鬥的大亨嘎卡的緣故，使得尤里再次復出參戰。後來，尤里被轉送往喬治亞；在那，他除了面對喜歡碎碎念並與自己不合的美國人托波外，還要和來自他國的囚犯們展開廝殺..<br />\n<br />\n9 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e5125ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=q3o5axvosZp8FsCNA2DpAozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=532b211b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/as